  Text: |-
    Fast UIs is a growing collection of programmatic UI multi-component compositions from UIKit.  Work with their own APIs or unpackage the FastUI package to modify the scripts further or provide a reference to your favorite AI tools and build UI fast. Often AI has an hard time understanding proportion across UI elements, this collection aims to mitigate that gap. 
    
    Zoom out to see more compositions or explore them in the scene hierarchy.   
